Producer!
Can I get off 'round here?

If it's ingredients for a bento,
I'll go to the supermarket.

You're amazin', Producer~!
How did ya know!?
Well, at lunch...

♪ Eggs, eggs~
Tamagoyaki, tomorrow's bento will be rolled~

♪ But since there are no more eggs~
Gotta go buy some~
You were singing something?

Fue...
Ya heard that!?

Producer, I was wearin' earphones and workin',
so I thought ya weren't listenin'...
You were just turning off the music at that point.

S-Sorry 'bout that... But, ya guessed right...
I'll ask at the supermarket~
Alright, got it.

Ah... Producer,
ya want somethin' to eat?

?
Like what?

After the festival's over,
I plan to treat everyone to some cookin'.

Since I want Producer to come too,
if ya have any requests, let me know~

Ah, I see... Since Kogane's making it,
maybe I should think about it a bit?

Of course! Anything ya wanna say!
I'll make it so delicious that your cheeks will drop!
